amp;andorexactfulltext=phrase\">TE, thioesterase</a></span></li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"license\" id=\"license-1\">\n          <p id=\"p-1\"></p>\n        </div>\n        <p id=\"p-3\" class=\"arthw-misc\">Fleming Prize Lecture 2007</p>","referencesHtml":"","affiliationsHtml":"<li class=\"aff\">\n\n              <address>\n                Department of Chemistry, University of Warwick, Coventry CV4 7AL, UK\n              </address>\n            </li>","correspHtml":"<li class=\"corresp\" id=\"corresp-1\"><strong>Correspondence</strong><br>\n            Gregory L. Challis<br>\n            <span class=\"em-link\"><span class=\"em-addr\">G.L.Challis{at}warwick.ac.uk</span></span></li>","pdfPath":null,"refdomains":0}